<li class="toclevel-2"><a href="#Philosopher_of_religion"><span class="tocnumber">3.2</span> <span class="toctext">Philosopher of religion</span></a>
<ul>
<li class="toclevel-3"><a href="#Anti-reductionism_and_the_.22transconscious.22"><span class="tocnumber">3.2.1</span> <span class="toctext">Anti-reductionism and the "transconscious"</span></a></li>
