<li id="cite_note-scnostal-4">^ <a href="#cite_ref-scnostal_4-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-scnostal_4-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-scnostal_4-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-scnostal_4-3" title=""><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-scnostal_4-4" title=""><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a> <span class="languageicon" style="font-size:0.95em; font-weight:bold; color:#555;">(Romanian)</span> Simona Chiţan, <a href="http://www.evz.ro/article.php?artid=263139" class="external text" title="http://www.evz.ro/article.php?artid=263139" rel="nofollow">"Nostalgia după România" ("Nostalgia for Romania"), interview with Sorin Alexandrescu</a>, in <i><a href="/wiki/Evenimentul_Zilei" title="Evenimentul Zilei">Evenimentul Zilei</a></i>, June 24, 2006; retrieved January 23, 2008</li>
